%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%AD-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BB%91-vi%E1%BB%85n-h%E1%BB%89/poem-MckcrDzR5IMVz8q99e9tfA">Tần Châu kiến sắc mục Tiết tam Cứ thụ tư nghị lang, Tất tứ Diệu trừ giám sát, dữ nhị tử hữu cố viễn, hỉ thiên quan kiêm thuật tác cư, hoàn tam thập vận - 秦州見敕目薛三璩授司議郎畢四曜除監察與二子有故遠喜遷官兼述 索居凡三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Thi-tr%C3%A1i/poem-7qDnDwdMicv_0DL0jXD4VA">Thi trái - 詩債</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Giang-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-smpQzQm0ln5VRnL2tbRYig">Trường Giang kỳ 2 - 長江其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%A9c-m%E1%BB%A5c/poem-AEH-nxDqoFxOiFAi7pWzOQ">Tức mục - 即目</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C5%A9-S%C6%A1n-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-t%C3%A1c-n%C3%AA/poem-Jh0ybTlYkxJlmL_djGuRGg">Vũ (Sơn vũ bất tác nê) - 雨（山雨不作泥）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
